title: Classic Goosebumps 15- Ghost Beach - R. L. Stine [Epub & Mob
description:
Ghost Beach
Author: R.L. Stine



Jerry can't wait to explore the dark, spooky old cave he found down by the beach. Then the other kids tell him a story. A story about a ghost who is three hundred years old. A ghost who comes out when the moon is full. A ghost . . . who lives deep inside the cave Jerry knows it's just another silly made-up ghost story . . . isn't it? It's our fifteenth fan-favorite companion to R.L. Stine's blockbuster Goosebumps HorrorLand series. Now with all-new bonus features including author secrets, urban legends, trivia, creepy quizzes, and more


Genre: Childrens | Fantasy
